   "source": [
    "# waitKey函数实现程序暂停"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 1,
   "id": "4010fa40",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [],
   "source": [
    "import cv2"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "code",
   "execution_count": 2,
   "id": "fcb029c4",
   "metadata": {},
   "outputs": [
    {
     "name": "stdout",
     "output_type": "stream",
     "text": [
      "触发了按键\n"
     ]
    }
   ],
   "source": [
    "lena = cv2.imread(\"../images/lena.bmp\")\n",
    "cv2.imshow(\"demo\", lena)\n",
    "key = cv2.waitKey()\n",
    "if key != -1:\n",
    "    print(\"触发了按键\")"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "6fbd7b6b",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "cv2.waitKey（）函数的参数值是默认值0，所以在未按下键盘上的按键时，程序会一直处于暂停状态。\n",
    "当按下键盘上的任意一个按键时，程序中key=cv2.waitKey（）下方的语句便得以执行，程序输出“触发了按键”。"
   ]
  }
 ],
